name: What's Chat Ui  (GB Version for Android)
description:
Do you want to direct message your family or friends, save status of your mobile contacts and enjoy much more amazing features? So, here is where GB version 22.0 for whatsapp comes in to solve this problem. GB version 22.0 for whatsapp provides amazing features like:


• Direct Message family or friends.

• Status saver

• Quick Reply

• Text Repeater

• Auto Respond
